### Get system status
GET http://localhost:5000/api/status

### Get latest readings for all sensors
GET http://localhost:5000/api/sensors/latest

### Get alerts for water quality issues
GET http://localhost:5000/api/sensors/alerts

### Get fresh reading for a specific region (replace Guwahati with any region)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/sensors/reading/Guwahati

### Manually simulate sensor data for all regions
POST http://localhost:5000/api/sensors/simulate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "region": "all",
  "force_alert": false,
  "data_source": "auto"
}

### Manually simulate sensor data for Shillong with forced alert
POST http://localhost:5000/api/sensors/simulate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "region": "Shillong",
  "force_alert": true
}
